  4. Confusion between gel polish, gel overlay, and gel extensions all being called "gel nails" at wildly different prices.
  5. Not knowing the realistic yearly cost of staying on a 2–3 week fill schedule.
- **exact_user_phrases:** "how much does it cost to get gel nails done at a salon"; "is gel manicure worth it"; "why does a manicure with gel polish cost so much more"; "how much to remove gel nails"; "hidden costs of maintaining gel nails"; "are gel or acrylic nails more expensive"; "how much is a full set of gel nails"; "gel nails so expensive"; "how much should I tip for gel nails"; "gel nail removal cost".
- **intent_content_signals:** Reader wants concrete dollar/pound ranges (not vague descriptions), a breakdown by region, an "add-ons that bump the price" list, and a direct gel-vs-acrylic-vs-dip cost comparison table.

